        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">West End's proximity to the CBD, its established lifestyle reputation and limited land supply make it a strong selling environment. The suburb's appeal to both owner-occupiers and investors provides a broad buyer pool that supports competitive sale conditions.</p>
